name: handle_new_user
definition:
CREATE OR REPLACE FUNCTION public.handle_new_user()
 RETURNS trigger
 LANGUAGE plpgsql
 SECURITY DEFINER
AS $function$
BEGIN
  INSERT INTO public.users (id, name, avatar_url)
  VALUES (
    NEW.id,
    COALESCE(NEW.raw_user_meta_data->>'name', NEW.raw_user_meta_data->>'full_name', 'User ' || substr(NEW.id::text, 1, 8)),
    NEW.raw_user_meta_data->>'avatar_url'
  );
  RETURN NEW;
END;
$function$
